author: adrianc
msg: First pass at overhauled Mini-language <set> element.
1. The schema has been updated to reflect the new syntax.
2. The updated element will log warnings for incorrect syntax. Validation logging can be turned off by changing the minilang.properties validation.level property to none.
3. The element will auto-correct the XML source file if the minilang.properties autocorrect property is set to true.
4. Code has been cleaned up and simplified.
